Sentencas: Nanosized incubational domain was observed in 10 at.% gadolinium-doped ceria (GDC) using high-resolution transmission electron microscopy.
Titulo: Dislocation Associated Incubational Domain Formation in Lightly Gadolinium-Doped Ceria

Sentencas: Dislocations were extensively observed in 10 at.% GDC instead of heavily doped 25 at.% GDC.
Titulo: Dislocation Associated Incubational Domain Formation in Lightly Gadolinium-Doped Ceria

Sentencas: By Fast Fourier Transform and Inverse Fast Fourier Transform analysis, it was noticed that the incubational domain existing in 10 at.% GDC has different lattice spacing and orientation from the neighboring ceria matrix.
Titulo: Dislocation Associated Incubational Domain Formation in Lightly Gadolinium-Doped Ceria

Sentencas: Furthermore, dislocations were usually observed in the interface region between the incubational domain and the ceria matrix.
Titulo: Dislocation Associated Incubational Domain Formation in Lightly Gadolinium-Doped Ceria

Sentencas: Based on experimental results, the formation mechanism of dislocation associated incubational domain in lightly gadolinium-doped ceria is rationalized.
Titulo: Dislocation Associated Incubational Domain Formation in Lightly Gadolinium-Doped Ceria
